Q5. Push your project to GitHub
================================================================================

STEP 1: Create a new repository on GitHub
-------------------------------------------
- Go to https://github.com
- Click "New Repository"
- Name it: my-project
- Keep it public
- Do NOT initialize with README (you already have one)
